/122161"><i>Encyclopédie Larousse</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ne.se/uppslagsverk/encyklopedi/lång/gunter-grass"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.munzinger.de/search/go/document.jsp?id=00000009590">Munzinger Archiv</a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://proleksis.lzmk.hr/24325"><i>Proleksis enciklopedija</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://snl.no/Günter_Grass"><i>Store norske leksikon</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.vle.lt/Straipsnis/gunter-grass"><i>Visuotinė lietuvių enciklopedija</i></a></li>
